Description: Model Context Protocol server for Zabbix integration
 A comprehensive MCP server providing complete access to Zabbix API
 functionality through the Model Context Protocol, enabling AI assistants
 and other tools to interact with Zabbix monitoring systems.
 .
 Features include:
  * Host, item, trigger, template, and user management
  * Problem, event, and maintenance management
  * Historical data and trend retrieval
  * Proxy and host group management
  * Read-only mode for secure monitoring
  * Support for both STDIO and HTTP transports
